description:
A bracelet that allows you to counterattack with powerful attacks.
[Response Change: Asault: Power/Range Weapon Dependent]
name: Assault Bracelet
note:
<srpgReactionSkill:30>
応戦の優先度は
ステート＞防具＞武器＞スキル＞エネミー＞
職業＞アクター＞プラグインのデフォルト
となっている。
腕輪と固有なら、固有の方が
優先度が上になる（後ろにあるため）。

description:
A bracelet that allows you to attack before your opponent in a counterattack.
[Response Change: Preemptive Strike: Attack Speed +2000/Range Weapon Dependent]
name: Strike Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that allows you to counterattack with long-range attacks.
[Response change: Shuriken: Range 2-4]
name: Shuriken Bracelet

description:
An assassin's bracelet that allows you to counterattack with poison attacks.
[Response change: Poison attack: "Poison" grant 50% / range weapon dependent]
name: Poison Blade Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that allows you to fight back with the magic "Burst".
[Response Change: Burst: Range 1-3 / Consumed MP 12]
name: Explosive Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that prioritizes defense over attack, allowing you to counterattack with defense.
[Response change: Defense: Damage reduction]
name: Protective Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that allows you to concentrate on avoiding your opponent's attacks rather than attacking.
[Response change: Dodge: Physical avoidance 25%]
name: Dodge Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that prevents state abnormality caused by opponent's attacks.
[Response change: abnormal defense: poison/paralysis/seal/dizziness/confusion/sleep]
name: Purifier Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that automatically heals wounds when attacked by an opponent.
[Response change: Regeneration: Self HP recovery]
name: Regeneration Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that increases your attack power when attacked by an opponent.
[Response change: Anger: Grants attack increase to self for 3 turns]
name: Rage Bracelet

description:
A bracelet that increases your own defense when attacked by an opponent.
[Response Change: Hardening: Give yourself a defense increase for 3 turns]
name: Solid Bracelet

description:
Clothing for adventurers that emphasizes ease of movement.
[Movement +1] [Defense Effect 80%]
name: Adventurer's Clothes

description:
Clothing worn by forest people. Lightweight as if you were wearing nothing.
[Movement +1] [Defense Effect 80%]
name: Ranger Clothes

description:
A robe worn by monks in training known for their martial arts.
[Movement +1] [Defense Effect 80%]
name: Fighter Clothes

description:
A jet-black costume worn by ninjas. Easier to dodge enemy attacks.
[Movement +1] [Defense Effect 80%] [Evasion Rate +10%]
name: Black Suite

description:
Battle uniforms worn by the elite troops of the eastern country. Both men and women can wear it.
[Movement +1] [Defensive effect 80%] [Physical damage reduction 20%]
name: Ryūhime Robe

description:
Armor for warriors made of layers of tanned leather.
[Max HP +4%] [Target rate 150%]
name: Hard Leather

description:
Heavy armor used by gladiators. Combines robustness and mobility.
[Max HP +8%] [Target rate 150%]
name: Duel Armor

description:
Heavy armor for knights with extravagant decorations.
[Max HP +12%] [Target rate 150%]
name: Caliber Mail

description:
Armor made from superimposed small dragon scales. Fire resistant.
[Maximum HP +16%] [Target rate 150%] [Fire reduction 50%]
name: Dragon Scale

description:
A lively armor for the brave, with mithril placed at its core.
[Maximum HP +20%] [Target rate 150%] [Magic damage reduction 20%]
name: Riburetto リブレット

description:
A robe for witches, woven with magical threads.
[Defensive effect 60%]
name: Wizard Robe

description:
A pure white robe that enhances magical power and is favored by priests.
[Defensive effect 60%]
name: White Garb

description:
A magical garment for court mages with intricate crests woven into it.
[Defensive effect 60%]
name: Mage Cloak

description:
Magnificent magic clothes made for battle maidens.
[Defensive effect 60%] [Movement +1]
name: Valkyrie Tier

description:
A traditional costume worn by female priests in eastern Japan.
[60% defense effect] [50% reduction in MP consumption]
name: Shrine Maiden Uniform

description:
A magical accessory with a divine protection that heals wounds.
[HP regeneration 10%]
name: Healing Ribbon

description:
Shoes with simple flight magic. Can move through holes and water.
[flight]
name: Wing Boots

description:
A ranger's foot ring infused with the divine protection of the spirit of the wind.
[Movement +1]
name: Wind Anklet

description:
A ring that envelops you in shadows and allows you to pass through enemies.
[Passing Through]
name: Shadow-Clad Ring

description:
A perfume that appeals to the opposite sex.
Demons are attracted. [Target rate 200%]
name: Finest Perfume

description:
A gauntlet that transforms "spirit" into a blade. Extends weapon range.
[Weapon Range +1]
name: Aura Blade

description:
Alchemy crystals. Extends the range of miracles and magic.
[Range of magic skills +2]
name: Sorcerer's Stone

description:
A cursed mask that grants great power in exchange for consciousness.
[All stats +20%] [Automatic battle]
name: Berserker Mask

description:
A necklace containing the prayers of the goddess of creation. Expand the owner potential.
[Reaction 50%]
name: Goddess Prayer

description:
Eastern swordsmanship. The name is "Saiha". Destroys the opponent's weapon when counterattacking.
[Response Change: Crush Blade: Grant "Armed Destruction" 25%]
name: Assassin's Dagger

name: Strong Defense

description:

name: Magic Barrier
